5698, "(fr)This is the Admiral. All ships signal battle readiness. Start the countdown timer to attack."

5699, "(fr)Kakotchka's digging in for a fight. Seeing a substantial point defense screen."

5700, "(fr)A bunch of gunboats and patrol craft. I'm only concerned with the real threat - that battlecruiser."

5701, "(fr)On my signal, Protogeneia is to move at flank speed at approach vector. Attack ships form up for CIWS defense."

5702, "(fr)All Commonwealth and Republique ships remain in position until I give the go ahead. Maintain group coherence."

5703, "(fr)LC Ross, you and Commander Anouilh are our fighter cover for the squadron. UAV wingmen will provide support."

5704, "(fr)That's a lot of ships out there, but I don't see the arsenal cruisers. No gravity ships either."

5705, "(fr)Kakotchka's holding them in reserve for the perfect time to strike. Bertini has to know the danger, doesn't he?"

5706, "(fr)All ships accounted for. We start the attack. Helm, take us to assault vector."

5707, "(fr)Rear Admiral Kakotchka. You are ordered to vacate Vicare and return the station to Sulsian control. [[This land is ours.]]"

5708, "(fr)This is Kakotchka. This space is no longer yours to tyrannise. The Free People of the Fringe deny your subjugation."

5709, "(fr)If you and your Commonwealth masters persist with your hostile action, we will respond as befits an act of war."

5710, "(fr)Will you listen to that self-important, self-righteous Weisenheimer. I'll bet she even believes her own propaganda."

5711, "(fr)Thank you LC, that will be quite enough. Orders are coming through from the Commodore. The squadron is moving to flank the Saragosse."

5712, "(fr)This whole attack feels wrong. You can't brute force against Kakotchka like this."

5713, "(fr)This is how Bertini fights. Brute and muscle. It's worked out for him so far."

5714, "(fr)Got movement from the Malikan pickets! They're burning straight towards the Sulsians."

5715, "(fr)Malikan skirmishers are in close proximity! We're having trouble establishing fire solutions!"

5716, "(fr)Incoming hostiles! Going for the merge!"

5717, "(fr)Contact! Two Malikan minelayers to starboard!"

5718, "(fr)This is carrier Diogeneia. The Malikans have attacked the Protogeneia with EMP mines. We've lost comms with the Admiral. "

5719, "(fr)Engine flares in the Vicare debris field! Combine strike craft powering up from cold start."

5720, "(fr)Incoming Combine LACs and strikers. Fighters and UAV drones, intercept and destroy."

5721, "(fr)All Commonwealth and Republique units, move to cover the Sulsian formation!"

5722, "(fr)Able 1, you can help the Sulsians where opportunity allows, but prioritise your cover of Commonwealth and Republique units."

5723, "(fr)Protogeneia, do you copy? Bertini! Get your ship clear. We'll cover you."

5724, "(fr)Those Malikan gunships are inbound towards Assurance. Take them out!"

5725, "(fr)The Protogeneia! She's going up!"

5726, "(fr)Commodore Lockerbie, I'm signalling our forces to retreat. Bringing impellers to spool."

5727, "(fr)All ships, cover the Sulsian retreat. Point defense target ASMs as a priority. Fighters, you're on floating defense."

5728, "(fr)The Protogeneia is gone. This is Captain Torres taking control of Sulsian forces. Escort ships form up around the Diogeneia."

5729, "(fr)Holy shit...!"

5730, "(fr)Assurance, why aren't we pressing the attack? Surely we've got the tonnage and numbers to get through!"

5731, "(fr)That Combine battlecruiser has enough firepower to challenge our squadron and we haven't got the strike craft cover. Maintain your defense Lieutenant Commander."

5732, "(fr)The Sulsians are in disarray. They need a covering screen or else none of them are going home."

5733, "(fr)We're getting massacred out here! Alban ships, cover us now!"

