5901, "(fr)Hostile fighters eliminated!"

5902, "(fr)We're coming up to Andaman. Got an urgent comms request from Station Control."

5903, "(fr)Inbound Commonwealth ship, be advised there are no available docking berths. Andaman station is on bypass due to lockdown."

