5943, "(fr)They're swarming us!"

5944, "(fr)Sir! Message from the hangar. Maintenance has cleared out our combat drones. They've been made flight worthy. We can launch them to help out against the fighters."

5945, "(fr)Area clear. Do we continue to Andaman Station?"

5946, "(fr)All fighters destroyed. No other hostile contacts for now."

5947, "(fr)Lieutenant Kelly, get me Andaman's master. I want our people off that station now."

5948, "(fr)This is Master Batra. I hear this is your fault the Combine have locked down my station. Who are these fugitives? Why have you got us involved in your war?"

5949, "(fr)Master Batra, listen to me very carefully. This lockdown is the fault of the Combine, and the Combine alone. They only care about getting what they want, and your station just happens to be an obstacle."

5950, "(fr)Obstacle? We become an obstacle as soon as we help you. We have no quarrel with the Archon. Why shouldn't I just let the Combine have these fugitives? What has the Commonwealth done for us?"

5951, "(fr)Because this is what a galaxy under Combine rule looks like. If you care at all about your people, this is our best chance of stopping that from happening."

5952, "(fr)This is how the Combine operate. They come to a system, lock it down and occupy it until they have no more use for it. I've seen them do it in Sulsia. They're doing the same thing here. They'll do it all again after this is over."

5953, "(fr)You ask what the Commonwealth's ever done for you? This! This is what we're doing. We're stopping them right here, right now! And you have a chance to help us do it."

5954, "(fr)All right, Alban. You say you're opposing the Combine? Show me. I'll have my security chief create a diversion in that section, make up an emergency to force the Combine to evacuate."

5955, "(fr)Your friends are near a transport berthed at C Dock. The way should be clear for them once the troops evacuate. In return, I want your ship to protect my station from any Combine warships once they find out what's going on."

5956, "(fr)Tell your people to move out in about two minutes. Hopefully we all get out of the other side of this in one piece."

5957, "(fr)High energy signals on approach! Two frigate-sized ships, with what look like strike craft escorts."

5958, "(fr)Well we got ourselves in the thick of it now. Stand by to engage new contacts."

5959, "(fr)Got confirmation of two Combine destroyers! Escorting striker wing and two LACs! They're closing in."

5960, "(fr)Sir! We're in range of their mass drivers!"

5961, "(fr)The bastards are firing at civilians!"

5962, "(fr)Stuart, this is Lau. We're making our way to the transport at Dock C. The dockmaster tells me we're good to launch in about one minute."

5963, "(fr)Don't launch yet! There are Combine warships near the docking rings. They'll fire on any transport leaving the station!"

5964, "(fr)Get in the transport but stay powered down. Await our signal to launch."

5965, "(fr)<sécurisé> Stuart, we're in the transport. Her pilot's standing by for your signal."

5966, "(fr)We need to stay out of range of those mass drivers or we'll get hammered!"

5967, "(fr)Striker wing peeling off to attack Aria!"

5968, "(fr)Stuart, what's happening out there? We've been advised that Combine troops are on their way to Dock C. We won't be able to hold them back for long."

5969, "(fr)Stuart! Combine soldiers are attempting to breach the transport airlock! We need to leave now!"

