5974, "(fr)Transport 5281 docking sequence complete. Passengers are able to disembark."

5975, "(fr)Sir, we've got confirmation that Lau and Erikson are on board Aria."

5976, "(fr)Thank God. Helm! We've done what we need to do. Get us a course out of here!"

5977, "(fr)Copy Lieutenant. Thank you. Thank you everybody. Helm, take us home."

5978, "(fr)Sir. I think that's everyone. Both destroyers neutralised. Escorting wings destroyed."

5979, "(fr)System exit vector calculated. Impellers ready."

5980, "(fr)Just keep believing in yourself, lad. Like I always told you. Everything else'll fall into place."

5981, "(fr)Destroyer mass drivers max range is 6000m"

